How LLMs Understand Prompts
LLMs don't read like humans, they process sequences of mathematical tables to perdict the most probable next output based on patterns learned during training.

Key Mechanism:
tokenization and prediction: the text is broken into chunks the model calculates the satastical probability of next token in the sequence.
Context Window: the maximum amount of text(input prompt + generated output) the model can retain it's working memory.
Attention Mechanism: It allows the model to weight the importance of different works in the prompt 
Role and structure: able to give the role to ai,structure sequence

